&nbsp;


  <p class="">Eligibility for the eyeglass prescription verification is based on an applicant’s age and state of residence. You can learn more about eligibility requirements <a href="https://new-eyes.org/visibly">here</a>.</p><p class="">Please note the online vision test is meant to verify an existing eyeglass prescription only. It does not replace a comprehensive eye examination and does not assess eye health.&nbsp; </p>























