  <p data-rte-preserve-empty="true" class=""></p><h2><strong>New Readers for Overseas Distribution</strong></h2><h2><strong><em>ReadingGlasses.com donates to help neediest overseas</em></strong></h2><p class="">New Eyes is grateful for corporate donations, like the one we’ve received from ReadingGlases.com.&nbsp; Thanks to their generosity, we will be receiving 5,000 pairs of readers, to be distributed via our Overseas Program!</p><p class="">"We often take so much for granted, including our eyesight,” said Peter Granoff, President and CEO of ReadingGlasses.com.&nbsp; “Something as simple as a pair of eyeglasses can be used to improve someone’s quality of life. ReadingGlasses.com is very pleased to help support New Eyes’ mission to bring glasses to those in need.”&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class="">Founded in 1986, ReadingGlasses.com is the world’s largest store for designer reading glasses.&nbsp;</p><p class="">For more information, visit: <a href="https://www.readingglasses.com/about-our-company/">https://www.readingglasses.com/about-our-company/</a></p><p class="">Thank you again for your donation!&nbsp;</p><p class=""><em>Note: While our Overseas Program has been suspended indefinitely due to COVID-19, we welcome donations of high need items like new, unused readers and sunglasses.</em></p>]]></description><media:content type="image/jpeg" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/53628c55e4b038197f765c8d/1602105058558-4CCYIQI6Y743AM5GQSD3/Readingglasses.com.jpg?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="1330"><media:title type="plain">Grateful Series:&nbsp;ReadingGlasses.com</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>Interns to the Rescue!</title><dc:creator>New Eyes for the Needy</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 17 Aug 2020 19:17:26 +0000</pubDate><link>https://new-eyes.org/blog/aug18-2020</link><guid isPermaLink="false">53628c55e4b038197f765c8d:5d8116ef505a1b02b25ed591:5f3abb7902ce222b56d5c06a</guid><description><![CDATA[How two brothers helped New Eyes get through the summer of 2020]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1>Thousands of Glasses, Hundreds of emails, Tens of Projects.</h1><h1>Two Interns.</h1>























