  <p class="">Join us today, on GivingTuesdayNow, a new day of global giving, created as an emergency response to the extraordinary need caused by coronavirus.&nbsp;</p><p class="">New Eyes has been receiving applications daily for new eyeglasses from people who have lost jobs or health insurance due to COVID-19. </p><p class="">We have served the most vulnerable during the Great Depression, World War II and the Great Recession of 2008.&nbsp; Please enable us to continue to serve during today’s crisis. </p><p class=""><strong>YOU</strong> will change lives with your gift by providing the clear vision necessary for adults to search for employment when the economy reopens. <strong>YOU</strong> will make a difference in the lives of children who need glasses for better home-schooling and remote education..</p><p class=""><a href="https://app.etapestry.com/onlineforms/NewEyesfortheNeedy/donate.html">Donate online here</a> or mail your donation to New Eyes at 549 Millburn Avenue, Short Hills, NJ 07078.&nbsp;</p><p class="">GivingTuesdayNow is an opportunity for people around the world to stand together in unity<em>—</em>let’s come together to bring clear eyesight to individuals who have little to no other resources to obtain eyeglasses, in these very difficult times.</p><p class=""><em>New Eyes</em> </p>























