  <p class="">Join New Eyes on GivingTuesdayNow, a new global day of giving and unity taking place next Tuesday, May 5, as an emergency response to the unprecedented need caused by COVID-19.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class="">It’s a day for everyone around the world to stand together and give back in all ways, no matter who or where we are.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class="">On GivingTuesdayNow, let’s support individuals - many who have lost their jobs or health insurance benefits due to COVID-19 - needing our help now more than ever.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class="">A $23 donation gives someone in the U.S. a new pair of eyeglasses and the clear vision required to navigate daily life; to find new work when the economy reopens; to have a better home-school experience.</p><p class="">At a time when we are all experiencing the pandemic, generosity is what brings people of all races, faiths, and political views together across the globe. Generosity gives everyone the power to make a positive change in the lives of others and is a fundamental value anyone can act on.&nbsp;</p><p class="">We look forward to seeing you on May 5!&nbsp;</p>]]></content:encoded><media:content type="image/png" url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/53628c55e4b038197f765c8d/1588192095423-OEHNO05QN47C85DASK3B/GTN+Save+the+Date-01.png?format=1500w" medium="image" isDefault="true" width="1500" height="1500"><media:title type="plain">Save the Date: GivingTuesdayNow - May 5,  A Global Response to COVID-19</media:title></media:content></item><item><title>Volunteer Spotlight:  Meet Janet, New Eyes’ Lens “Detective” </title><dc:creator>New Eyes for the Needy</dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2020 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate><link>https://new-eyes.org/blog/april20-20</link><guid isPermaLink="false">53628c55e4b038197f765c8d:5d8116ef505a1b02b25ed591:5e8f7ce51610114444bf5918</guid><description><![CDATA[“These eyeglasses will transform someone’s life, and I’m proud to be a part 
of that,”]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[&nbsp;










































  

    
  
    

      

      
